Signatures.Label: Table(record/table, ...)
Signatures.Documentation: Creates a table from the specified records and tables, with as many columns as there are unique record fields. For example: Table({key1: val1, key2: val2, ...}, ...)

Parameters.Label: record/table
Parameters.Documentation: A record/table that will be part of the the resulting table.
